title: 12/24/21  DPS Hour 3  Doug Gottlieb & Jason McIntyre Guest Hosting - Adam Caplan
itunes:title: 12/24/21  DPS Hour 3  Doug Gottlieb & Jason McIntyre Guest Hosting - Adam Caplan
description:
Doug and Jason have a spirited discussion about the NBA super teams and if they have made a dent in the general interest of the NBA. The guys give their NFL picks for the weekend. And FSR Insider Adam Caplan joins Doug and Jason to get listeners ready for a week 16 filled with covid and injury absences.
